codex
Implemented the designer save/apply collapse.

- `persistActiveSurface` no longer takes a mode parameter and always POSTs to `/api/metadata/designer/:entity/:surface/apply` in [`packages/ui/platform/designer-context.tsx`](/home/ubuntu/slopware/packages/ui/platform/designer-context.tsx#L945).
- Removed the separate `saveDesign` path from the designer context API and command registration in [`packages/ui/platform/designer-context.tsx`](/home/ubuntu/slopware/packages/ui/platform/designer-context.tsx#L198).
- F10 now triggers `applyDesign()` and only closes the designer after a successful apply in [`packages/ui/platform/designer-context.tsx`](/home/ubuntu/slopware/packages/ui/platform/designer-context.tsx#L1753).
- The InlineDesigner panel now has a single Save action that always applies, with the separate Apply button removed in [`packages/ui/components/inline-designer.tsx`](/home/ubuntu/slopware/packages/ui/components/inline-designer.tsx#L164) and [`packages/ui/components/inline-designer.tsx`](/home/ubuntu/slopware/packages/ui/components/inline-designer.tsx#L430).

Validation:
- `pnpm lint` passed with 0 errors.
- Lint still reports 3 existing warnings in `packages/ui/components/entity-mask.tsx`, unrelated to this issue.

<promise>NO MORE TASKS</promise>
